title: 30 minut (a cover, org. t.A.T.u)
info:
2003. An AY ZX Spectrum chiptune from AY-RIDERS album "Do you remember?". 
Download link: http://ay-riders.speccy.cz/download/do_you_remember/19-Yerzmyey-30minut_Remix(org_TATU).mp3
The song was the main promotion tune of the independent American animation movie "We are the strange".
